pageContext.description: 3 short vertical ribs on the faces.  edge chipped, also three mouldings as well as the rim, round the mouth.  there is quite a deep groove just above the points of the edge which disappears after 1/2 cm.  Expanding edge., Surface: fairly smooth on the top side, there is a powdering of bright green like many of the Lakenheath objects.,  Patina:  Otherwise the patina is dark green with some metal showing through.
